import Mathlib

open Complex Metric Finset

theorem jirilebl_ca_ca_12552 :
  ∀ (f : ℂ → ℂ), AnalyticOn f (Metric.closedBall (0 : ℂ) 1) → f 0 ≠ 0 →
  ∃ (p : FormalMultilinearSeries ℂ ℂ ℂ) (C : ℝ),
    HasFPowerSeriesAt f p 0 ∧ p.coeff 0 ≠ 0 ∧
    ∀ (m : ℕ) (z : ℂ), Complex.abs z ≤ 1 →
      Complex.abs (1 - ∑ k in range (m + 1), (p.coeff k) / (p.coeff 0) * z ^ k) ≤ C * (Complex.abs z) ^ (m + 1) := by
  sorry
